SIMPLE: tongueless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tongueless
<hw>Tongue"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
no tongue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, speechless; mute.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧What
<xex>tongueless</xex> blocks were they! would they not speak?⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Unnamed; not spoken of.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One good deed dying <qex>tongueless</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tonguelet</ent>⟦br⟧
